BASICS
 - cdk init --language typescript : start a demo repo in the current folder
    - bin/cdk-demo.ts : entry point
    - lib/cdk-demo-stack.ts : define your stack here
 - aws sts get-caller-identity : get account id
 - aws configure get region : get current default region
 - npm install @aws-cdk/aws-ec2 : install ec2 module
